            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "JG International School is amazing! The teachers are always ready to help us and are really very approachable, making it easy for us to ask questions. The school helps us build important communication and public speaking skills, which are super helpful further in our life.\n\nWe get to participate in fantastic events like Model United Nations (MUN) conferences and TEDx talks, allowing us to express our talents and gain confidence, and not only participate but also host such event providing with various opportunities.\n\nThe principal is very supportive of students and ensures that we have a positive learning environment. The school’s mission focuses on helping us discover our potential and providing the support we need to grow into successful global citizens.\n\nLearning at JGIS is exciting and encourages us to be active, curious learners. Overall, JG International School is a great place to learn, grow, and prepare for the future!\n\nThank You very much for these excellent years at JGIS from Nursery till IBDP-II. JGIS is always has been my second home and always will be.\n\nThank You to Principal ma'am and all the teachers to mould us in such a way that we are excellent learner's and knowers.",
