            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It has been wonderful studying in this school. It has everything from book fairs to carnivals. As a student, I love studying in this school. The food  is very hygienically and scrumptiously served. The class teachers and subject teachers also engage and interact with us a lot. The syllabus is quite huge but the teachers help us cover it without taking a lot of burden. Discipline is also maintained by both teachers and students very nicely. The school is quite vast with numerous activities coming and going round. It also provides first aid and medical help whenever needed as there is  a full time nurse in the medical room and it also has medical checkups. This is the best school in the whole of INDIA. EVERYONE MUST COME TO THIS SCHOOL.😘",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
