          "reviewBody": "JGIS is a wonderful school with a very dedicated staff and management. The school conducts numerous activities for all round development of children. Each teacher is deeply involved in the progress of every child. Facilities like food, sports and activities are fantastic. The management is warm and approachable. The academic year has numerous events and the children also get additional academic support. JG is a great all round school and has been a definitive milestone for my kids. All the best to the staff and management!",
